COA RemoteRest validation flow

0. Before running Postman

Run this query and capture the current ATTEMPTS values:

SELECT
    a.SPONSOR_ID,
    r.SPONSOR_NAME,
    a.PROOFING_LEVEL,
    a.KBA_SUPPLIER_ID,
    s.KBA_SUPPLIER_NAME,
    a.TOTAL_ATTEMPTS,
    a.ATTEMPTS,
    a.UPDATE_DATE
FROM IPS_OWN.RP_KBA_ATTEMPTS a
JOIN IPS_OWN.REF_SPONSOR r
    ON r.SPONSOR_ID = a.SPONSOR_ID
JOIN IPS_OWN.REF_KBA_SUPPLIER s
    ON s.KBA_SUPPLIER_ID = a.KBA_SUPPLIER_ID
WHERE a.SPONSOR_ID = 32
  AND a.PROOFING_LEVEL = 1
ORDER BY a.KBA_SUPPLIER_ID;

Expected after your fix:

ATTEMPTS should not change after transactions.

